3.2 Design and Simulation Using SolidWorks\par
\b0 Using the 3D CAD models, we created several design iterations of the mounting structure. The SolidWorks platform allowed us to simulate the structural integrity and performance of the designs, including stress analysis and vibration testing. We also optimized the Field of View (FOV) of the LIDAR sensors to ensure maximum operational efficiency, accounting for various sensor angles and mounting positions. By conducting these simulations, we were able to refine the design, ensuring that the mounting structure met the required specifications for stability and flexibility.\par
\par
