\pard\sa200\sl276\slmult1\b 3.4 Fabrication and Integration\b0\par
Following the validation of the prototype, the next step was to fabricate the final mounting structure using aluminum profiles, chosen for their strength-to-weight ratio and corrosion resistance. The structure was fabricated with precision, ensuring that it met the design specifications derived from the simulations and prototypes. Once fabricated, the mounting structure was integrated with the UGV and the LIDAR sensors. This integration process was carefully managed to ensure that all components fit together seamlessly and that the sensors were securely positioned for optimal performance.\par
