3.5 Testing and Evaluation\par
\b0 Finally, extensive testing was conducted to evaluate the performance of the mounting structure. This included testing the alignment and stability of the sensors, as well as verifying the Field of View (FOV) of the LIDAR sensors under different operating conditions. The testing phase also involved assessing the flexibility of the structure in accommodating different sensor configurations and adjusting the mounting positions for optimal sensor coverage.\par
